{"tid":2105214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[算帳中]中西區區議員何致宏稱涉管有危險藥物遭送往柴灣警署","createTime":"2020-07-12T13:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T13:28:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88b09866ef3d9055fc330ec23204e7a88001ff06","tid":2105214,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"中西區區議員何致宏在社交專頁表示被捕，他的專頁上載的影片顯示，他在西灣河太安樓對開被幾名軍裝警員反鎖雙手，並帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n何致宏有份參與民主派立法會選舉初選，排在南區區議員彭卓棋名單第二，彭卓棋接受本台訪問時表示，何致宏在西灣河拉票時被捕，涉嫌管有危險藥物，被送往柴灣警署。<br />\n<br />\n本台已向警方查詢事件，暫未回覆。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537335-20200712.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537335-20200712.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=ee8ff431\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537335-20200712.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fae640ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537335-20200712.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3cc57fe8e9bacdf425ebbfef49b0320ae00be41f","tid":2105214,"uid":60924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哮喘藥"},{"pid":"bd06cd2189ab33a1058f6886b2d65f52bc9b840c","tid":2105214,"uid":345502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88b09866ef3d9055fc330ec23204e7a88001ff06","tid":2105214,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T13:08:31.000Z","msg":"中西區區議員何致宏在社交專頁表示被捕，他的專頁上載的影片顯示，他在西灣河太安樓對開被幾名軍裝警員反鎖雙手，並帶上警車。<br />\n<br />\n何致宏有份參與民主派立法會選舉初選，排在南區區議員彭卓棋名單第二，彭卓棋接受本台訪問時表示，何致宏在西灣河拉票時被捕，涉嫌管有危險藥物，被送往柴灣警署。<br />\n<br />\n本台已向警方查詢事件，暫未回覆。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537335-20200712.ht